Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:11.15,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}您所拨打的电话暂时无法接通或是已关机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经去打工了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要走得这么快?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要跑?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间可能在秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这边～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽间她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不要…芽间消失!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳如果死掉…绝对绝对不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是都死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说奇怪应该是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:19:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲤鱼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河里啊 有条很大很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间啊 因为想靠近点看…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在树桩那里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地游呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 在撒娇吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你留在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你抓鲤鱼过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仁碳 会弄湿的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 笨蛋仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
